WEBVTT

00:01.591 --> 00:04.695
I thought Activia was for big digestive issues,...

00:04.943 --> 00:07.453
...until I realized our body handles a lot.

00:07.817 --> 00:10.037
1100 meals a year.

00:10.973 --> 00:12.798
730 rush snacks.

00:13.993 --> 00:16.245
Add 300 stressful decisions.

00:17.011 --> 00:20.167
No wonder our digestive system sometimes acts up.

00:20.731 --> 00:22.615
So, try the Activia challenge.

00:22.921 --> 00:24.954
Enjoying Activia twice a day for four weeks...

00:25.024 --> 00:27.652
...may help reduce the frequency of bloating, gas, discomfort or rumbling.

00:27.907 --> 00:29.399
It works, or it's free.

